name: East of Eden
description: '''East of Eden''' were a British [[progressive rock]] band, who had a [[Top 40|Top 10]] hit in the UK with the single "[[Jig-a-Jig (song)|Jig-a-Jig]]" in 1970. The track was stylistically unlike any of their other work. Although some might consider them a symphonic progressive band, others state that their style is mostly [[jazz]]-oriented.
